OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA pleasant
OL,6,Fevening with widespread sunshine and
OL,7,Feasing winds for many, followed by a
OL,8,Fmostly clear and cool night. Remaining
OL,9,Fbreezy along north Norfolk coasts.
OL,10,
OL,11,CFriday:FVariable cloud on Friday, but
OL,12,Fplenty of sunny spells through the
OL,13,Fday. Warm to very warm in the
OL,14,Fsunshine. Clouding over in the late
OL,15,Fafternoon and evening. Light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
